{"tid":169890,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"聰明豆的消失","createTime":"2017-03-24T12:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T13:59:19.000Z","uid":4747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d159e94719e1f70106afa757e356f6d7c1d468cc","tid":169890,"uid":4747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"重記得細細個 同老母行超巿既時候<br />\n<br />\n每當見到朱古力都會叫老母買<br />\n<br />\n有幾種我係特別鍾意食既 <br />\n<br />\nM&amp;M 、三角朱古力、同埋聰明豆<br />\n<br />\n依家我唯一搵到有聰明豆既地方就只得老麥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「乜你咁蠢架，食多啲聰明豆啦！」相信大家都聽過類似既說話<br />\n<br />\n於是我想問 邊度重有聰明豆賣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c51b98ad247f6470bc4ccdbf0d826a600d5d67","tid":169890,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:37:26.000Z","msg":"老麥無左Smartee好耐"},{"pid":"ba55d7a3c5a6f96a6d21cb46af410104cc99a62f","tid":169890,"uid":4747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T12:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老麥無左Smartee好耐</blockquote><br />\n其實都係一年左右啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02fdda9163adf212bf35dcbb29dbd3088d02c84e","tid":169890,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"優品360 大量"},{"pid":"93a9c01559d0fc72370521652d434a2604948616","tid":169890,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"唔用意譯用音譯（斯蜜提斯），費事意譯名違反《商品說明條例》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}